<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Paul Sturm, Bürger zu Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat verweist wegen der Vorwürfe gegen Peter Haller und Konrad Eschenloher auf den Rechtsweg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_88" id="43r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_88_r1l22">Pauls Sturm </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_88_r1l23">Pauls Sturm als du vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt wie dıch Peter <expan>hall<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l24">vnd der Eſchenloer beſchedıgt <expan>ſüll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> recht etc / da ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l25">vns niht <expan>wıſſenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von / vvıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> hettſt du ʒu <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l26"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ıcht <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dır gleıch vnd rechts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l27"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen als <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> / vves du denn recht haſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_r1l28">des <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dır wol gunnen / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>ıs</expan> tucher </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_88_line_1577026524997_4736"><expan>ſe<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">orıs</hi></expan> <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıcuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> / <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>p<ex>ur</ex>ıfıca<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>ıs</hi></expan> marıe </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_88" id="43r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Pauls Sturm </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Pauls Sturm, als du uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hast wie dich
                                                Peter <expan>Hall<ex>er</ex></expan> und der
                                                Eschenloer beschedigt <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> recht etc., da ist uns
                                                niht <expan>wissenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Von wie
                                                  <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> hettst du zu
                                                  <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>zu
                                                  spreche<ex>n</ex></expan>, so
                                                  <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir dir gleich und
                                                rechts <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen als
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgern</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich</expan>, wes du denn
                                                recht hast, des <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                                dir wol gunnen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo
                                                  <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>is</expan> Tucher
                                                  <expan>se<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">oris</hi></expan>
<expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri
                                                  civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>p<ex>ur</ex>ifica<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>is</hi></expan> marie.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
